---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---
<Layout title="Project">
    <main class="pt-24 pb-20">
        <!-- hero section : project identity -->
         <section class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-8 mb-16">
<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-end justify-between gap-8">
<div class="max-w-3xl">
<div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
<span class="bg-primary/10 text-primary px-3 py-1 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest rounded-sm">Industrial Safety</span>
<span class="text-secondary text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">ID: PRJ-2024-BPN</span>
</div>
<h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black tracking-tighter text-on-surface leading-tight mb-6">
                        Instalasi Sistem Proteksi Kebakaran Kilang Minyak Balikpapan
                    </h1>
<p class="text-lg text-secondary leading-relaxed font-medium max-w-2xl">
                        Implementasi menyeluruh sistem pemadam otomatis berbasis NFPA untuk infrastruktur strategis energi nasional. Menjamin keberlanjutan operasional dengan presisi teknis tingkat tinggi.
                    </p>
</div>
<div class="pb-2">
<a class="flex items-center gap-2 text-primary font-bold text-sm group" href="#">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-lg">arrow_back</span>
<span class="group-hover:underline underline-offset-4">Kembali ke Portofolio</span>
</a>
</div>
</div>
        </section>

        <!-- bento gallery -->
         <section class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-8 mb-24">
<div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-4 h-[600px]">
<div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-8 relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-surface-container">
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover" data-alt="wide angle shot of massive industrial oil refinery infrastructure at dusk with complex piping and warm safety lighting" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAF_6Pwy0rcd3nhaDMBZ80xza6x_COwa4bp01wzifADwH_jOYAqA8iSOZTYAc5fyZv4DrYD29oTNhPdoFmsk1LN4zi0NNiqSKYPR-e2KzKZuSyTmLXXbM4-CZAAS-pWOwOsWEw7pn2tc__WLMZT1DWsg70wXCQ5ne2MhdDxp3-_oNqTSXFt6uUVCJrsOHvAOGhdcei-1HIzz3n2fp_NNqCTpCriuEVR9lcvueaPmf5FDesl5nyNhqZeyjub05agt_MtoA3Jj78M8is"/>
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent"></div>
<div class="absolute bottom-6 left-6 text-white">
<p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest opacity-80 mb-1">Main Site</p>
<h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Zona Pengolahan Utama</h3>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-4 grid grid-rows-2 gap-4">
<div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-surface-container">
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover" data-alt="close up of red industrial fire protection pipes and high pressure valves in a clean factory environment" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuA0YJow8fJtkZ16WjoxM0e8KFtMmhcHgrNyQaTmV4QykcfJUI3Gmo6QuoRQfBIbEteVG_rnibJ7Vyr8YTI5MlnyCRmtsBvaxKG475dn1ECeQgYy5zNmKrNqt27auA6p3aljYz0tDzkx28m7W_1Bkg_MdAYlVc1QRMr7R-8AAjIF5bq22wxYxWJzV_qArdse9YwvB1qZ7y5RjXG9HQBFtIKALHr6hz2CjaGRc9AeDiLuxn5lEn07sOPRLP1faitDSndntbFAbOnjF4g"/>
</div>
<div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-surface-container">
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover" data-alt="engineer in reflective vest inspecting complex electrical and mechanical control panels for fire safety system" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDr3oXoni7tmV0hxoRuzDeKBE94a4h7AqMlBTFmrCwvTPTYoZcBHNLFU6BZaVvYf9KYYIiSuLh81vJtgZvDkfbE5ljNVbU4CMok73CG6pHxoPhpc-CtM8F79DXp7nF2O_pw70PJYC0uMuL72Txi4UyXgbrf2V3gNvdiHJ2l0KlLbEb9D6ZN6bgraMRCE0Ar7rL9uy9keOOyfU48PiO8X96UojMcjRHP4tCfRKvXeb2CYh7Vffzu695Byav_RErRfEf1WZrQLB9BJng"/>
</div>
</div>
</div>
        </section>

        <!-- technical specs -->
         <section class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-8 grid grid-cols-12 gap-12 mb-32">
<div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-5">
<div class="sticky top-32">
<span class="text-primary font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] block mb-4">Technical Blueprint</span>
<h2 class="text-4xl font-black tracking-tighter mb-12">Spesifikasi Proyek &amp; Standar Teknis</h2>
<div class="space-y-6">
<div class="p-6 bg-surface-container-low rounded-lg border-l-4 border-primary">
<h4 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase text-secondary tracking-widest mb-2">Kapasitas Sistem</h4>
<p class="text-xl font-bold text-on-surface">50,000 GPM Foam-Water System</p>
</div>
<div class="p-6 bg-surface-container-low rounded-lg border-l-4 border-tertiary">
<h4 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase text-secondary tracking-widest mb-2">Regulasi Kepatuhan</h4>
<p class="text-xl font-bold text-on-surface">NFPA 11, 15, &amp; 20 Standard</p>
</div>
<div class="p-6 bg-surface-container-low rounded-lg border-l-4 border-secondary">
<h4 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase text-secondary tracking-widest mb-2">Durasi Pengerjaan</h4>
<p class="text-xl font-bold text-on-surface">18 Bulan (Q3 2022 - Q1 2024)</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-7 pt-12 lg:pt-0">
<div class="bg-white p-12 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-outline-variant/10">
<h3 class="text-2xl font-black mb-8 flex items-center gap-3">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">engineering</span>
                        Tantangan &amp; Solusi Strategis
                    </h3>
<div class="space-y-12">
<div class="relative pl-8 border-l-2 border-surface-container-highest">
<div class="absolute -left-[9px] top-0 w-4 h-4 bg-primary rounded-full"></div>
<h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">Integrasi Infrastruktur Eksisting</h4>
<p class="text-secondary leading-relaxed">Penyambungan sistem proteksi baru ke dalam infrastruktur kilang yang sudah beroperasi selama puluhan tahun tanpa menghentikan proses produksi (Hot Tapping).</p>
</div>
<div class="relative pl-8 border-l-2 border-surface-container-highest">
<div class="absolute -left-[9px] top-0 w-4 h-4 bg-primary rounded-full"></div>
<h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">Lingkungan Korosif Tinggi</h4>
<p class="text-secondary leading-relaxed">Penggunaan material Stainless Steel 316L dan coating khusus untuk menghadapi atmosfer pesisir Balikpapan yang memiliki salinitas tinggi.</p>
</div>
<div class="relative pl-8 border-l-2 border-surface-container-highest">
<div class="absolute -left-[9px] top-0 w-4 h-4 bg-primary rounded-full"></div>
<h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">Logistik Material Oversize</h4>
<p class="text-secondary leading-relaxed">Manajemen pengiriman tangki foam konsentrat vertikal dengan kapasitas 15.000 liter melalui jalur laut dan instalasi menggunakan crane kapasitas 250 ton.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
        </section>

        <!-- testimoni -->
         <section class="bg-surface-container-low py-24">
<div class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-8">
<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-16">
<div class="w-full md:w-1/3">
<div class="relative">
<img class="rounded-2xl grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-500 shadow-xl" data-alt="portrait of a middle aged male executive in professional business attire with industrial background" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCw6IR1DRIFFRFX6I0m7kyjB_2rRMMoa8-NpqcKWpdU7gqBLDQhVwCUde6wdxb8tSvm19TD6GbVhfcG5GONGtGUdbo7PmhA9GrD6PsagiFfow2SBMkSd1YdiDBjqm1LBiygAmclDmY2_d1bXD45QxMEjeo66IASP0BDlBlmksg6seYPVHX5D23QrWie0u2T7A-XdGteG6ceaVzXJJ3lInN4Aox0vF2ufvCGFz2AlgCcrnj1p55taab6XdaSCGAaslury9bUClD5Hs4"/>
<div class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 bg-primary p-6 text-on-primary">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl">format_quote</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="w-full md:w-2/3">
<span class="text-primary font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] block mb-6">Client Voice</span>
<blockquote class="text-3xl font-light italic leading-snug text-on-surface mb-8">
                            "Profesionalisme tim APAR Engineering dalam menangani proyek kritikal di Balikpapan sangat luar biasa. Ketepatan waktu dan kepatuhan terhadap standar NFPA memberikan kami ketenangan operasional yang tak ternilai."
                        </blockquote>
<div>
<p class="text-xl font-bold">Ir. Bambang Setyawan</p>
<p class="text-secondary font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-sm">Sr. Project Manager - Energy Infrastructure Div.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
        </section>

        <!-- final CTA -->
         <section class="py-32 text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto px-8">
<h2 class="text-4xl font-black tracking-tighter mb-8">Siap Membangun Standar Keamanan Baru untuk Fasilitas Anda?</h2>
<div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
<button class="bg-primary text-on-primary px-8 py-4 rounded-md font-bold shadow-md hover:scale-105 transition-transform">
                    Konsultasi Teknis Gratis
                </button>
<button class="bg-white text-on-surface px-8 py-4 rounded-md font-bold border border-outline-variant/30 hover:bg-surface-container-low transition-colors">
                    Unduh Katalog Proyek
                </button>
</div>
        </section>

    </main>
</Layout>